      "text": "Functional Req.\n\n    ! Convert analog \n    to digital samples\n    ! Feed them to Rust\n    ML and get meaningfull\n    data\n    ! Send data stream to API\n    including self status\n    ! Able to update firmware\n    upon request (searching for a \n    way to avoid buying domain \n    names)\n    ! Logging\n    ",
